snippet.title: Bridges & Piers by Armesto | Content Creator Pack | Cities: Skylines
snippet.description:
Enhance and elevate your waterfronts with unique assets from community creator Andrés “Armesto.” Bridges & Piers features 12 new bridges, 8 new quay styles, and 2 new piers. With styles ranging from simple to ornate and industrial to classical looks found around the world.

Get it on Steam today: http://pdxint.at/brpi

Check out Armesto on the Steam Workshop: https://steamcommunity.com/id/armesto/myworkshopfiles/
